<h2 id="make-it-anything-you-want">Make it anything you want</h2>
<blockquote>
  <p>Never forget that you can make your role anything you want it to be. Anything you hate to do, someone else loves. So find that person and let her do it.</p>
</blockquote>

<h2 id="why-i-gave-my-company-to-charity">Why I gave my company to charity</h2>
<blockquote>
  <p>Kurt Vonnegut and Joseph Heller were at a party at a billionaire’s extravagant estate. Kurt said, “Wow! Look at this place! This guy has everything!” Joseph said, “Yes, but I have something he’ll never have…Enough.”</p>
</blockquote>
